item.title: Cache wont Download
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

Chances are you may not have zipped it correctly.
And also make sure to use the direct download link. So if you place the link in browser, it will start the download as soon as you hit enter (or go).

Can’t provide more help without the errors seen in the Console.
